3. INSTALLATION

The library depends on:
 * ErrUt, which can be found at
   http://research.edm.uhasselt.be/jori/errut/errut.html
 * ENUt, which can be found at
   http://research.edm.uhasselt.be/enut/enut.html
 * SerUt, which can be found at
   http://research.edm.uhasselt.be/jori/serut/serut.html

Just use the configure script and make to build the library. Run the 
configure script with option '--help' to see which options can be 
specified.

